Key Match Events: Chet Holmgren suffered a right iliac wing fracture during the game.
Holmgren fell on his hip after attempting to contest Andrew Wiggins.
Holmgren was helped off the court and did not return to the game.
Post-Match Reflections: Chet Holmgren expressed his frustration and determination to return stronger after his injury.
Holmgren addressed OKC fans and family from the hospital bed, emphasizing his passion to return.
